{"tid":1193772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荔枝角道男子墮樓　被困工廈外牆","createTime":"2019-06-09T05:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T05:11:27.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"96f0ba0023a8dd21ef8b8eb2b51463d82cbfab56","tid":1193772,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T05:11:27.000Z","msg":"荔枝角工廈有人墮樓。今午(9日)12時05分，一名男子在荔枝角道808號一工廈高處墮下，倒臥於7至8樓之間重傷昏迷，被困在外牆。消防接報到場，將事主救下，由救護車送院搶救。警方正調查事主身份及墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=%2BD6XGwqev%2FlZKpArKwvoHSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=5f81e79e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190609/mobile/bkn-20190609124053351-0609_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190609%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190609124053351-0609_00822_001.html&d=%2BD6XGwqev%2FlZKpArKwvoHSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=7a0be77f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190609/mobile/bkn-20190609124053351-0609_00822_001.html</a>"}]}